            <p>Agni TMT Steels: Building Strength Since 1890
      
              Agni TMT Steels, established in 1989, has made significant progress over the past three decades, emerging as a
              leading steel producer in South India. Initially a supplier of raw materials and a trade organization, Agni TMT
              Steels soon expanded into a major integrated steel plant renowned for its commitment to quality in the private
              sector. Agni TMT Bars are the hallmark of the Agni brand, celebrated throughout South India.</p>
          </div>
          <br>
          <div class="abtus2p">
            <p>As one of the most reputed steel companies in South India, Agni TMT Steels operates two state-of-the-art
              rolling mills in Tamil Nadu and an iron-making plant in Andhra Pradesh. Headquartered in Chennai, Tamil Nadu,
              the company specializes in manufacturing a variety of steel bars, including TMT, CRS, and Ready-Made Rings
              (RMS). These products, available in diameters of <span style="color: yellow;">6mm, 8mm, 10mm, 12mm, 16mm, 20mm,
                and 25mm,32mm</span> are extensively used in construction and civil works.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
