      <div class="history">
        <u class="heading">HISTORY</u>
        <br>
        <img src="/images/scooty.jpg">
        <p  >
          The story of Agni TMT Steels is a testament to the power of perseverance and vision. It all began with a humble scooter, which played a pivotal role in the company's inception. In the early days, our founders relied on this modest vehicle to travel extensively across the region, visiting various steel manufacturing facilities. These journeys were not merely about travel but were filled with learning and discovery. The founders sought to gain a deep understanding of the steel manufacturing process, observe best practices, and gather crucial knowledge about the industry's intricacies.</p>
<br>
<p >Every visit, every conversation, and every observation contributed to a growing repository of expertise. Armed with this wealth of knowledge and experience, our founders were inspired to embark on an ambitious journey. They envisioned creating a steel manufacturing company that would stand out for its quality, innovation, and commitment to excellence. Thus, in 1989, Agni TMT Steels was born, symbolizing the transformation of dreams into reality.</p>
<br>
<p >The scooter, which was a simple means of transportation, became a symbol of our humble beginnings. It represented the grit, determination, and relentless pursuit of knowledge that laid the foundation for Agni TMT Steels. Over the next three decades, the company grew from a modest startup into a leading name in the steel industry. This journey was marked by significant milestones, including the establishment of state-of-the-art rolling mills, the introduction of advanced manufacturing technologies, and the consistent production of high-quality steel bars.</p>
<br>
<p >Agni TMT Steels' growth and success are a reflection of our founders' vision and the values they instilled in the company. From those early days of traveling on a scooter to visit steel plants, we have scaled remarkable heights, becoming a trusted name in the industry. Today, Agni TMT Steels is renowned for its superior products, robust quality assurance processes, and unwavering commitment to customer satisfaction.</p>
